title: Alf Wilson (boxer)
text: Alf Wilson (born 1909, date of death unknown) was a South African <a href="boxing">boxer</a>. He competed in the <a href="Boxing%20at%20the%201928%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20middleweight">men's middleweight</a> event at the <a href="1928%20Summer%20Olympics">1928 Summer Olympics</a>.
